sing the following syntax, run the **DaRT Recovery Image Wizard**. *NumberOfDays* is a positive integer that represents the number of days that the DaRT recovery image will be usable.\n\n    ``` syntax\n    ERDC /e NumberOfDays\n    ```\n\n## Related topics\n\n\n[Creating the DaRT 7.0 Recovery Image](creating-the-dart-70-recovery-image-dart-7.md)\n\n \n\n \n\n\n\n\n\n"}